	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sessiones recepi, domine et frater colendissime, nec scio, quorum culpa postremo in tuas manus venerint, cum volueram, ut in tuas et <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastii</persName> primum venirent.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si hic aliquando ingratus aut iniquus in me fuit, id nescivi hactenus; certe fideliter curat omnia, quae illi committo, quibus sane honoris causa te oneratum nolo.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magno cum animi mei dolore tibi nuncio piissimum et doctissimum symmystam fratrem meum charissimum d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8459" cert="high">Otthonem Werdmullerum</persName> heri in noctis principio ad horam nonam e tenebris huius saeculi sana fide migrasse ad lucem illam aeternam.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optime quidem cum ipso factum fatentur omnes, qui his liberatus et molestiis et malis, quae dominus ommit[t]et ingratissimo huic saeculo; sed nobis interim symmystis et fratribus maximum reliquit maerorem.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scis, qualis fuerit, pius, beneficus, modestus, diligens et solide doctus et mei imprimis amans.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus, qui dat ecclesiae suae doctores et pastores, alium in locum eius sufficiat ecclesiae suae utilem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bellum hoc <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germanicum</placeName> secundum ita me excrutiat ut nihil aeque.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Multa metuo; si Caesar prior occuparit <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentoratum</placeName>, brevi mira videbis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam, utinam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germani</placeName> adhuc agerent poenitentiam; utinam nos omnes ardentiores ad dominum preces funderemus et vitam pessimam mutaremus; non enim erit ulla salus in equitatu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallico</placeName> aut peditatu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germanico</placeName>, sed in misericordia dei nostri.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid agant et consultent Pagani, dubito, scio autem certissimo illos sui similes futuros, donec etc.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ingentem dolorem concipio ex moribus nostris nec aliud expecta quam infanda mala.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus misereatur nostri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libellum meum nuper missum te accepisse spero, eum puto, quo purgo ecclesias nostras a labe haereseos et schismatis etc.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te fratres et mei imprimis generi tres, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7228" cert="high">Zvinglius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1888">Lavaterus</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8442" cert="high">Simlerus</persName>, affinis <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherus</persName> et domini ac fratres <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodorus</persName>, <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Gessnerus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3988" cert="high">Wolphius</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1214" cert="high">Frisius</persName> etc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">26. martii 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Osvaldo Myconio</persName>, <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basiliensis</placeName> ecclesiae fido pastori, domino et fratri suo colendissimo et charissimo.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
